reviewText: Item arrived quickly. Good series.
I love NCIS and these characters are wonderful lots of excitement suspense and laughter. Some of the plastic that holds the CDs came broken not happy about that.
Love this show!  Can't wait to get Season 7 set.
Awesome

EVEN THOUGH I DON'T CARE FOR THE NEW NCIS, NEW ORLEANS, I LOVE NCIS, LOS ANGELES.  THIS SIX SEASON PACKAGE COMPLIMENTS MY DVD COLLECTION OF THE REGULAR NCIS AS WELL AS OTHER "COP" SHOWS.  MY ONLY REGRET IS IT'S NOT YET AVAILABLE IN BLUE RAY.
Great Tv series plenty of action and a good story line I would recommend this Tv series especially if you like Special Ops  or Cop type movies
Arrived on time and in new condition. The price was good, and I look forward to binge watching this series.
Omg, I'm so glad I got this season. It was awesome. Everything was packaged perfectly and no damage to the DVD's.
They all came in great condition and I got every single one of them!!
thank you
Great DVD set, great quality, arrived in a timely manner
Love the show and so does my 83 year old neighbor. Got them so he could see all without commercial interruptions.

I am rating this a 3 because although the shipment came quickly all but one of the seasons were intact. Season 3 was damaged and the case was completely destroyed!

So i am updating my review. I received my replacement series and all looks to be in order so I feel a 4 is justified.

This is a great series...very slow in the first 3/4 of season one then cast changes are made & better story lines are written & all of a sudden it's up to the caliber of the original NCIS. I hung in there because Linda Hunt is exceptional from the pilot & I am so glad I did. As for the shipping of the DVD's...Amazon did what it always does and shipped all seasons (1-6) taped together in a stack with no packaging in a box. So all boxes are cracked/missing pieces down the center where you would open the cases. Predictable.
am a fan of all ncis,s. this just completed my collection.
Just started to get the total series. One collection at a time.
One of the disk won't play. It has markings on it.
This show is outstanding.  I have all of their shows.  Great product.
I have tried watching NCIS:LA Season 5, but the 1st disc will not play on any of my Bluray players. I am will let you know as I play the rest & which will not play
All of the season came in nice new sealed cases. I gave this to my wife for Christmas and she just loved it.  Thank you LL Cool J for providing the entire six season  set in one order.
I brought as a gift for my father-in-law. He loved it!
What can I say, seen em once, great to see the story line and pick up what I missed the first few times.
Love this show!!
Awesome Thank you.!!!

The DVD quality is very good. The show is very enjoyable. The characters are well thought out and bring the idea of a true work force. This show brings detective work and the "con" together in a very enjoyable format.
